title: Atari byiza ko umubyeyi yakongera gutwita mbere y’uko umwana ate agira nibura imyaka ibiri mu rwego rwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwabo.
content: Atari byiza ko umubyeyi yakongera gutwita mbere y’uko umwana ate agira nibura imyaka ibiri mu rwego rwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwabo. Umubiri w’umubyeyi ukibyara ukenera kuruhuka; akarya neza kugira ngo agarure imbaraga n’ubuzima bwiza mbere y’uko yongera gutwita.
